      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA TURBO (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.65) in a Grade 5 H at this track. Has ability and is a key runner. FLAMING SMOOTH (2) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (25.46) last time in a Grade 5 H at Shepparton. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Better than last start and can bounce back. FRENZY (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (30.43) at this track behind Ivory Inzai in a Grade 5. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Winning chance. PAW TARKOV (4) won from this box last start so keep him in mind.",
